milast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, Belimumab, More', 'Pertuzumab, Vismodegib, Enasidenib, Belzutifan, Sonidegib, Mitotane, Porfimer sodium, Estramustine, Aminolevulinic acid, Tazemetostat, Vorinostat, More', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/121995/', '[1] "Product Information. Arava (leflunomide)." Hoechst Marion-Roussel Inc, Kansas City, MO.', 1767369485);
